Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.94,0:01:35.64,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}知曉你的強大的
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.00,0:01:41.42,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}人的希望  無名之人
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.72,0:01:46.22,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}讚頌你的內心吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.49,0:01:52.08,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}淡淡的小花們
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.41,0:01:57.22,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}堅韌不撓的藤蔓的形狀
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.88,0:02:02.64,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}懷中藏有刺的影子
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.11,0:02:09.62,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}各自懷著不可言喻的昨天
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.62,0:02:13.37,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}向天空而去
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.77,0:02:18.83,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}只要生命還在  就喊出願望吧
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.14,0:02:24.33,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}心意終將貫穿星辰
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.55,0:02:29.62,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}在漫長又短暫的時間的盡頭
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.93,0:02:32.17,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}你生存過的
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.17,0:02:34.07,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}證據會
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.63,0:02:37.05,OPED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1}頂起土壤
